    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
