        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the chicken and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
