      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> udon noodles</strong> to the pan, gently separating them with a fork</p><p>Once separated add the <strong>gochujang sauce</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further, stirring until the noodles are coated in the sauce and your chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
